videos.headline: Hilarious celebration blunder after Southern Illinois' first TD
videos.description: QB Sam Straub finds TE Nigel Kilby in the end zone, and Raphael Leonard gets a little too excited about the Salukis' early lead.

videos.headline: Ole Miss responds with 7-yd TD run
videos.description: Rebels RB Scottie Phillips finds daylight and ties the game at 7.

videos.headline: Southern Illinois fires right back with TD run
videos.description: QB Sam Straub links up with WR Braylon Sanders to make it 14-7 Salukis.

videos.headline: Ole Miss WR climbs ladder for game-tying TD
videos.description: Rebels QB Jordan Ta'amu throws it up, and WR Braylon Sanders brings it down for a 30-yard touchdown reception to knot the game at 14.

videos.headline: Southern Illinois scores third TD of 1st quarter
videos.description: QB Sam Straub powers his way to the end zone to put the Salukis back on top, 21-14.

videos.headline: Ta'amu on the money for 50-yd TD pass
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Jordan Ta'amu connects with WR Elihaj Moore, who takes it the distance and evens it up at 21.

videos.headline: Ta'amu goes deep again for go-ahead TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu drops it in to WR A.J. Brown for 38-yard touchdown, giving the Rebels their first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Southern Illinois goes back on top
videos.description: QB Sam Straub converts in the red-zone and throws a 9-yard touchdown pass to WR Raphael Leonard.

videos.headline: Ole Miss reclaims lead on TD run
videos.description: Rebels RB Scottie Phillips punches it in from six yards out to give Ole Miss a 35-31 lead.

videos.headline: Southern Illinois turns botched snap into 70-yd TD
videos.description: QB Sam Straub regathers a bad snap to find TE Raphael Leonard, who makes a man miss and tiptoes down the sideline for a 70-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss recaptures lead on 46-yd TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu goes deep and hooks up with WR A.J. Brown, who reaches for the pylon and puts the Rebels ahead 42-38.

videos.headline: Ta'amu extends Ole Miss' lead with red-zone TD
videos.description: WR D.K. Metcalf goes up and gets a 5-yard touchdown pass from Jordan Ta'amu, giving the Rebels some breathing room.

videos.headline: Ole Miss DB goes 88 yards for pick-6
videos.description: DB Vernon Dasher jumps in front of a Sam Straub pass and takes it all the way back, making it 55-41 Rebels.

videos.headline: Ole Miss runs it in to build lead
videos.description: RB Isaiah Woullard keeps his legs moving for a hard-earned 2-yard TD run to make it 62-41 Rebels.

videos.headline: Rebels' defense creates scoop-and-score
videos.description: Ole Miss defenders Jacquez Jones and Ross Donelly knock the ball free, and DE Victor Evans takes care of the rest for another defensive touchdown.
